<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 10:08:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>报告称，以色列正在讨论使用海水淹没加沙隧道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/israel-debating-using-seawater-to-flood-gaza-tunnels-report-says/0000018c-3909-dc03-a9ec-3d7b120a0000</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，以色列为此目的组装了一个大型水泵系统，并于上个月向美国提交了该计划。埃及过去曾成功地利用海水淹没加沙隧道，但由于所有人的目光都集中在以色列，一些人对后果和国际反应表示担忧</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 09:42:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/israel-debating-using-seawater-to-flood-gaza-tunnels-report-says/0000018c-3909-dc03-a9ec-3d7b120a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡腐败审判的法官接受因战争而减少听证会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/judges-in-netanyahu-corruption-trial-accept-reduction-of-hearings-due-to-war/0000018c-393d-d11b-a3bf-ffbd56ee0000</link><description>审判的最后一次听证会于 9 月举行，此后法庭因节日休庭。 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击后，整个法院系统暂停了除紧急案件外的所有诉讼程序，包括对总理的审判</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 09:26:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/judges-in-netanyahu-corruption-trial-accept-reduction-of-hearings-due-to-war/0000018c-393d-d11b-a3bf-ffbd56ee0000</guid></item><item><title>强奸作为战争武器：犹太妇女呼吁联合国对抗哈马斯的性暴力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-and-jewish-women-implore-a-reticent-un-to-confront-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018c-369b-dc03-a9ec-3efbfcb90000</link><description>经过备受批评的沉默之后，联合国召开了首次特别会议，讨论 10 月 7 日大屠杀期间“有预谋和有计划”使用性暴力的问题。发言者包括希拉里·克林顿、谢丽尔·桑德伯格和以色列官员，他们介绍了迄今为止收集到的证据</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 09:24:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-and-jewish-women-implore-a-reticent-un-to-confront-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018c-369b-dc03-a9ec-3efbfcb90000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯被释放的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2023-12-05/ty-article-magazine/the-hostages-released-from-hamas-captivity/0000018c-0fb3-d65f-a7dd-fff736090000</link><description>100 多名以色列人和外国人质于 10 月 7 日在加沙被绑架后已获释或获救。这份确认的名单将不断更新</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 08:51:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2023-12-05/ty-article-magazine/the-hostages-released-from-hamas-captivity/0000018c-0fb3-d65f-a7dd-fff736090000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队挺进加沙南部，逼近主要目标：哈马斯辛瓦尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-thrusts-into-southern-gaza-and-closes-in-on-its-main-target-hamas-sinwar/0000018c-36b5-dc03-a9ec-3eff4d9a0000</link><description>两个月的战斗已经大大削弱了哈马斯的实力，但底线是它仍在继续战斗，并且没有表现出任何愿意放下武器的迹象</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 04:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-thrusts-into-southern-gaza-and-closes-in-on-its-main-target-hamas-sinwar/0000018c-36b5-dc03-a9ec-3eff4d9a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队袭击加沙北部哈马斯安全总部；三名士兵在战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article-live/idf-gearing-up-for-ground-offensive-in-southern-gaza-hamas-says-death-toll-tops-15-800/0000018c-37f5-d11b-a3bf-f7fd02e20000</link><description>报告：以色列考虑淹没哈马斯地下隧道的计划 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部表示，自停火结束以来，已有 316 名巴勒斯坦人被杀 ■ 以色列国防军公布了周日在加沙战斗中丧生的三名士兵的姓名 ■ 21 岁的以色列思想在加沙被绑架被宣告死亡 ■ 以色列军队表示，自加沙地面行动开始以来，已找到 800 个哈马斯隧道竖井 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列境内至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵被杀；加沙仍有超过 137 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙至少有 15,899 人死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 03:20:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article-live/idf-gearing-up-for-ground-offensive-in-southern-gaza-hamas-says-death-toll-tops-15-800/0000018c-37f5-d11b-a3bf-f7fd02e20000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-36f1-dc03-a9ec-3efb02a20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 22:30:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-36f1-dc03-a9ec-3efb02a20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列阿拉伯人被要求给出一些明确的答案。这里有一些</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israeli-arabs-are-being-asked-to-give-some-clear-answers-here-are-a-few/0000018c-3662-de12-a3af-3fefda8b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 22:06:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israeli-arabs-are-being-asked-to-give-some-clear-answers-here-are-a-few/0000018c-3662-de12-a3af-3fefda8b0000</guid></item><item><title>不乏敌人，只有巴以友谊才能解决这个烂摊子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/with-no-shortage-of-enemies-only-palestinian-israeli-friendships-can-fix-this-miss/0000018c-3662-de12-a3af-3fefdb2e0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 22:04:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/with-no-shortage-of-enemies-only-palestinian-israeli-friendships-can-fix-this-miss/0000018c-3662-de12-a3af-3fefdb2e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡选民之战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-war-for-netanyahus-voters/0000018c-3662-d5f2-a5cc-7676d68d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 21:49:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-war-for-netanyahus-voters/0000018c-3662-d5f2-a5cc-7676d68d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列营救人质的时间不多了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/israel-is-running-out-of-time-to-rescue-the-hostages/0000018c-3662-d5f2-a5cc-7676d2320000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 21:46:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/israel-is-running-out-of-time-to-rescue-the-hostages/0000018c-3662-d5f2-a5cc-7676d2320000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯卫生部称，自与以色列停火协议结束以来，加沙已有数百人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/hundreds-killed-in-gaza-since-truce-with-israel-ended-hamas-run-health-ministry-says/0000018c-3653-d11b-a3bf-f6fbc1440000</link><description>周一晚上，加沙市汗尤尼斯的居民报告说，以色列军队对该市进行了异常猛烈的轰炸，以色列国防军正在为加沙地带南部的地面进攻做好准备</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 20:50:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/hundreds-killed-in-gaza-since-truce-with-israel-ended-hamas-run-health-ministry-says/0000018c-3653-d11b-a3bf-f6fbc1440000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军预备役军人在恐怖袭击后开枪打死以色列男子，涉嫌鲁莽杀人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/idf-reservist-arrested-for-shooting-israeli-man-during-jerusalem-terror-attack/0000018c-3485-dc03-a9ec-3cffbea00000</link><description>以色列军警逮捕了预备役士兵阿维亚德·弗里贾（Aviad Frija），他认为被枪杀的犹太男子是袭击耶路撒冷公交车站的巴勒斯坦恐怖分子之一。极右部长：“民族英雄”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 19:37:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/idf-reservist-arrested-for-shooting-israeli-man-during-jerusalem-terror-attack/0000018c-3485-dc03-a9ec-3cffbea00000</guid></item><item><title>加沙南部的恐怖景象：每平方公里18,000人断水断电</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/south-gazas-horror-scenario-18-000-people-per-square-km-without-water-or-power/0000018c-353e-dc03-a9ec-3d7fd74f0000</link><description>任何支持对汗尤尼斯发动地面进攻的以色列人——包括政治家——都必须记住，战后最终数据将放在世界上每一位外交部长和媒体的办公桌上</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 18:47:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/south-gazas-horror-scenario-18-000-people-per-square-km-without-water-or-power/0000018c-353e-dc03-a9ec-3d7fd74f0000</guid></item><item><title>亲巴勒斯坦抗议者瞄准犹太名厨拥有的费城沙拉三明治店</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/pro-palestinian-protesters-target-philadelphia-falafel-shop-owned-by-jewish-celebrity-chef/0000018c-3607-d3ba-af9f-ff27c6ff0000</link><description>大费城犹太联合会的两名高管表示，“仅仅因为以色列和犹太人的所有权而针对企业是公然的反犹太主义”。白宫表示针对此类餐厅是“反犹太主义且完全没有道理的”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 18:43:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/pro-palestinian-protesters-target-philadelphia-falafel-shop-owned-by-jewish-celebrity-chef/0000018c-3607-d3ba-af9f-ff27c6ff0000</guid></item><item><title>前拜登官员警告加沙迫在眉睫的人道主义灾难</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/ex-biden-official-warns-of-humanitarian-disaster-in-gaza/0000018c-35b2-d5f2-a5cc-77b6ec630000</link><description>难民国际主席杰里米·科宁迪克“非常担心”加沙正处于由战争本身以外的因素造成的第二波重大死亡浪潮的风口浪尖，他毫不羞于批评拜登政府的行为</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 18:05:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/ex-biden-official-warns-of-humanitarian-disaster-in-gaza/0000018c-35b2-d5f2-a5cc-77b6ec630000</guid></item><item><title>以色列左翼活动分子在保护以定居者为目标的西岸村庄时遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/left-wing-israeli-activists-attacked-while-protecting-settler-targeted-west-bank-village/0000018c-35c4-d5f2-a5cc-77d471c10000</link><description>其中一名活动人士头部受伤，脸部和肋骨都有瘀伤，另一名活动人士则被喷了胡椒喷雾。自加沙战争爆发以来，由于定居者的暴力和威胁，活动人士一直在村庄里睡觉</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 17:56:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/left-wing-israeli-activists-attacked-while-protecting-settler-targeted-west-bank-village/0000018c-35c4-d5f2-a5cc-77d471c10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教授在不太可能的战争中以学术换取农业领域</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-professors-swap-academic-for-agricultural-fields-in-unlikely-war-effort/0000018c-353a-d5f2-a5cc-773ec4c90000</link><description>哈马斯在 10 月 7 日的大屠杀中杀害了至少 40 名来自泰国的移民工人，之后又有数千人逃离该国。响应求助号召，学者们正在离开象牙塔，踏入加沙边境社区的现实生活</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 17:47:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-professors-swap-academic-for-agricultural-fields-in-unlikely-war-effort/0000018c-353a-d5f2-a5cc-773ec4c90000</guid></item><item><title>《国土报》等媒体如何在针对以色列和哈马斯的假新闻战争中被武器化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/how-media-outlets-like-haaretz-are-weaponized-in-the-fake-news-wars-over-israel-and-hamas/0000018c-3076-d15f-a7af-b27664390000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击以来，互联网上充斥着各种影响力行动，这些行动放大了假新闻并劫持《国土报》等可靠的新闻来源，以给人一种否认暴行和阴谋论的真实感觉。这就是新闻业如何被虚假信息战所利用</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 17:42:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/how-media-outlets-like-haaretz-are-weaponized-in-the-fake-news-wars-over-israel-and-hamas/0000018c-3076-d15f-a7af-b27664390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列儿科医生表示，哈马斯扣押的儿童人质遭受“可怕的心理虐待”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/hamas-held-children-hostages-under-terrible-psychological-abuse-pediatrician-says/0000018c-3520-dc03-a9ec-3d7b543a0000</link><description>照顾从哈马斯囚禁中获释的以色列儿童的医生分享了有关情况的信息，他说：“这些是我从大屠杀幸存者祖父那里听到的故事。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 15:28:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/hamas-held-children-hostages-under-terrible-psychological-abuse-pediatrician-says/0000018c-3520-dc03-a9ec-3d7b543a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>